name: CSSframework
tagline: Simple CSS framework to help users style their page
body:
### CSSframework project
This CSS framework is a project that helps users to develop web applications. Please feel free to clone/fork our project. You can start by cloning this repository in your terminal:

```
$ cd git clone https://github.com/PHPsimple/CSSframework.git
```
### Authors and Contributors
This project is maintained by @PHPsimple and @loopByte is the main contributor to this repository. If you have trouble with this project feel free to open issues on the repository issues.
